text: The 19th Sarawak State Legislative Assembly is the upcoming term of the Sarawak State Legislative Assembly, the legislative branch of the Government of Sarawak in Sarawak, Malaysia. The 19th Assembly will consist of 82 members that are to be elected in the next state election. The term will last for five years from the first sitting. == Notes == == References == Category:Sarawak State Legislative Assembly
title: 19th Sarawak State Legislative Assembly
